title: Seydiler
text: Seydiler is a town and district of the <a href="Kastamonu%20Province">Kastamonu Province</a> in the <a href="Black%20Sea%20Region%2C%20Turkey">Black Sea</a> region of <a href="Turkey">Turkey</a>. According to the 2000 census, population of the district is 5,269 of which 3,254 live in the town of Seydiler. The district covers an area of , and the town lies at an elevation of .
